265
00:21:02,380 --> 00:21:04,045
Ternyata dia ibunya Yoo Yu-jin.

266
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:08,145
[ Han Mi-young Menikahi Lim Chul-yong ]

267
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:13,815
Kang Min-suk dan Yoo Hyo-myoung tewas,

268
