Hei.

272
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:33,405
Kurasa kalian bekerja dengan baik.

273
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,705
Apa?

274
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,679
Jung-tae, kembalilah ke Nonyang.

275
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,315
Tetaplah di sana sampai kutelepon.

276
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,349
Joo-hyuk, satukan ini untukku.

277
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,485
Baik, Pak.

278
00:21:47,990 --> 00:21:51,525
Kini akhirnya aku bisa
memahami Lim Chul-yong.

279
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:06,075
Semalam, beberapa orang asing datang

280
