281
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:10,005
- Aku dan Byeol-na?
- Ya!

282
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:11,745
Mereka bahkan menunjukkan beberapa foto

283
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:13,975
dan semuanya mirip Byeol-na.

284
00:22:14,550 --> 00:22:16,345
Itu pasti keluarganya, 'kan?

285
00:22:18,090 --> 00:22:19,985
Bukankah itu bagus?

286
00:22:20,060 --> 00:22:21,225
Tapi masalahnya,

287
00:22:22,460 --> 00:22:24,085
mereka tampak agak mencurigakan.

288
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,649
[ - Pak!
- Sebelah sini! ]

289
00:22:46,650 --> 00:22:48,789
- Tolong beri komentar!
- Kau mengaku berselingkuh?

290
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:51,359
